in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/scroll_event\"><code>scroll</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectionchange_event\"><code>selectionchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectstart_event\"><code>selectstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchcancel_event\"><code>touchcancel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchend_event\"><code>touchend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchmove_event\"><code>touchmove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchstart_event\"><code>touchstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/visibilitychange_event\"><code>visibilitychange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Zusammenfassung","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>Lesbar, nicht schreibbar</strong></p>\n\n<p>Gibt das&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a>&nbsp;zurück, das&nbsp;die Wurzel des&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document\">document</a></code>&nbsp;ist (zum Beispiel, das&nbsp;<code>&lt;html&gt;</code>&nbsp;Element für HTML Dokumente).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var&nbsp;<em>element</em> = document.documentElement;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> rootElement <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>documentElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> firstTier <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> rootElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>childNodes<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// firstTier ist die NodeList von direkten Kindern des Wurzel-Elementes</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> firstTier<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token comment\">// hier irgendwas mit den direkten Kindern des Wurzel-Elementes mit Hilfe</span>\n   <span class=\"token comment\">// von firstTier[i] erledigen</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Beobachtungen","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Objekt ist lesbar aber nicht schreibbar. Es ist praktisch um auf die Wurzel eines beliebigen Dokumentes zuzugreifen.</p>\n\n<p>HTML Dokumente enthalten typischerweise ein einziges Tochter-Element<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">, </span><code style=\"font-style: normal; line-height: 1.5;\">&lt;html&gt;</code><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">, manchmal mit einem DOCTYPE. XML-Doumente enthalten oft mehrere Tochter-Elemente, einen DOCTYPE und&nbsp;</span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\" style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">Verarbeitungshinweise</a><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">.</span></p>\n\n<p>Deswegen sollte&nbsp;<code>document.documentElement</code>&nbsp;statt <code><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/firstElementChild\"><code>document.firstElementChild</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></code>&nbsp;benutzt werden, um auf das Wurzel-Element zuzugreifen.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-87CD092\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: Document.documentElement</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Zusammenfassung","id":"summary"},{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"example"},{"text":"Beobachtungen","id":"notes"},{"text":"Spezifikation","id":"specification"}],"summary":"Lesbar, nicht schreibbar","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document.documentElement","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"document.documentElement","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"document.documentElement","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document.documentElement","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Document.documentElement","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"document.documentElement","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Document.documentElement","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Document.documentElement","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"document.documentElement","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Document.documentElement","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/document/documentelement","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/document/documentelement/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Document","title":"Document"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Document/documentElement","title":"document.documentElement"}],"pageTitle":"document.documentElement - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}